10:T56a,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"A Certain Scientific Railgun S","description":"The second season of <i>Toaru Kagaku no Railgun</i>.<br>\n<br>\nSomething sinister is going on in Academy City. The shadows are filled with whispers of an organization cloning super-powered students known as espers. High-ranking master of electricity, Mikoto Misaka, laughs off these stories until she comes face to face with a copy of herself. After learning that these clones - her sisters - are being systematically murdered in a series of experiments designed to turn a sadistic killer into the strongest esper in history, Misaka vows to save her copies and destroy the organization responsible for the project.<br>\n<br>\nAs Misaka prepares to face off against the organization’s power-hungry esper, she discovers that she wasn’t the only victim of the scientific forces conspiring within the city - and that’s something Misaka and the girls of Judgement simply won’t stand for.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx16049-FbOhOsQAuisF.jpg","datePublished":"2013-04-12","numberOfEpisodes":24,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["Action","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":7.9,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"f59de7aa-0896-4b6c-ac3b-a91d1024a14c","tmdb_id":16049,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"A Certain Scientific Railgun S","original_title":"とある科学の超電磁砲S","overview":"The second season of <i>Toaru Kagaku no Railgun</i>.<br>\n<br>\nSomething sinister is going on in Academy City. The shadows are filled with whispers of an organization cloning super-powered students known as espers. High-ranking master of electricity, Mikoto Misaka, laughs off these stories until she comes face to face with a copy of herself. After learning that these clones - her sisters - are being systematically murdered in a series of experiments designed to turn a sadistic killer into the strongest esper in history, Misaka vows to save her copies and destroy the organization responsible for the project.<br>\n<br>\nAs Misaka prepares to face off against the organization’s power-hungry esper, she discovers that she wasn’t the only victim of the scientific forces conspiring within the city - and that’s something Misaka and the girls of Judgement simply won’t stand for.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)","poster_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/nx16049-FbOhOsQAuisF.jpg","backdrop_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/16049-J5FVFQgBKp1p.jpg","release_date":null,"first_air_date":"2013-04-12","status":"published","original_language":"ja","origin_country":["JP"],"genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action"},{"id":2,"name":"Fantasy"},{"id":3,"name":"Sci-Fi"}],"popularity":92596,"vote_average":7.9,"vote_count":null,"runtime":24,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":24,"created_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:35.705958+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:35.666+00:00","tagline":null,"homepage":null,"budget":null,"revenue":null,"production_companies":[{"name":"J.C.STAFF"}],"production_countries":null,"spoken_languages":null,"networks":[],"last_air_date":"2013-09-27","in_production":false,"tmdb_status":"Ended","content_rating":null,"keywords":[{"id":1,"name":"Super Power"},{"id":2,"name":"Urban Fantasy"},{"id":3,"name":"Female Protagonist"},{"id":4,"name":"Urban"},{"id":5,"name":"Primarily Female Cast"},{"id":6,"name":"Superhero"},{"id":7,"name":"Primarily Teen Cast"},{"id":8,"name":"Bisexual"}],"alternative_titles":null,"videos":[],"watch_providers":null,"wikidata_id":null,"tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-05-02T08:50:35.70595